</div></div></section></section><section id="floats-group1" class="floats-group"><section class="bt xbox font-sm" id="BX1"><h2 class="obj_head">HIGHLIGHTS.</h2>
<ul id="L2" class="list" style="list-style-type:disc">
<li><p id="P62">We explore a generalizability assessment method using electronic health record data.</p></li>
<li><p id="P63">The method controls for eligibility criteria, recruitment time, and clinical setting.</p></li>
<li><p id="P64">The method compares trial participants to potentially eligible patients.</p></li>
<li><p id="P65">Granular comparisons can be performed to better explore clinical differences.</p></li>
</ul></section></section><section id="S17" class="ack"><h2 class="pmc_sec_title">Acknowledgments</h2>
